## JavaScript小技巧之Check if a string contains another string as a substring in JavaScript

- String.prototype.includes() function
- String.prototype.indexOf() function
- String.prototype.search() function
- Lodash Library _includes

### String.prototype.includes() function

```javascript
var source = 'Hello World';
var target = 'llo';
console.log(source.includes(target));
```

### String.prototype.indexOf() function

```javascript
var source = 'Hello World';
var target = 'llo';
console.log(source.indexOf(target) !== -1);
```

### String.prototype.search() function

```javascript
var source = 'Hello World';
var target = 'llo';
console.log(source.search(target) !== -1);
```

### Lodash Library _includes

```javascript
var source = 'Hello World';
var target = 'llo';
console.log(_.includes(source, target));
```

